<body class="bg-white text-black font-body leading-normal personality-casual">
  <Nav />

  <main class="py-12 lg:py-20">
    <!-- component -->
    <div class="py-16 bg-white">  
    <div class="container m-auto px-6 text-gray-600 md:px-12 xl:px-6">
        <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-0 md:flex md:gap-6 lg:items-center lg:gap-12">
            <div class="md:5/12 lg:w-5/12">
            <img src="/images/2022_nikola_sarajevo.jpeg" alt="image" loading="lazy" width="" height="">
            </div>
            <div class="md:7/12 lg:w-6/12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 font-bold md:text-4xl">{title}</h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600">As a curious generalist by nature, I wear many hats. I've been around, seen things. With over 14 years of experience working at the intersection of research and industry, I know the ropes. I'm a pro at research enablement, business support, and innovation management. I've been advisor to the management of swiss fintech startup <a href="https://numarics.com/" target="_blank">Numarics</a> and currently serve as the growth lead at cloud development environments pioneer <a href="https://codeanywhere.com/" target="_blank">Codeanywhere</a>.</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">I've helped companies grow, created successful new products, pricing strategies, and inbound campaigns. I'm a mentor to startups, a judge at startup events, EU project evaluator, and project manager on projects with a cumulative value over 34 million EUR. I was European IP Helpdesk ambassador.</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">I'm working to build innovation systems and support entrepreneurial and innovative researchers and companies. In short, I'm a master of growth and innovation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <EmailSignup />
  <Footer />
</body>

</html>